<refentry id="cvar.team_maxMortars">

<refmeta>
    <refentrytitle>team_maxMortars</refentrytitle>
    <manvolnum>cvar</manvolnum>
</refmeta>

<refnamediv>
    <refname>team_maxMortars</refname>
    <refpurpose>sets the maximum number of mortars per team</refpurpose>
</refnamediv>

<refsynopsisdiv>
    <cmdsynopsis>
        <command>team_maxMortars</command>
        <arg><replaceable>num</replaceable></arg>
    </cmdsynopsis>
    <cmdsynopsis>
        <command>team_maxMortars</command>
        <arg><replaceable>num</replaceable>%</arg>
    </cmdsynopsis>
</refsynopsisdiv>

<refsection>
<title>Default</title>
    <cmdsynopsis>
        <command>team_maxMortars</command>
        <arg choice="plain"><literal>-1</literal></arg>
    </cmdsynopsis>
</refsection>

<refsection>
<title>Description</title>
<para>
    <command>team_maxMortars</command>
    sets the maximum number of mortars each team can have at once.
    Setting <replaceable>num</replaceable> to <literal>-1</literal> allows for unlimited mortars.
    Setting <replaceable>num</replaceable> to <literal>0</literal> disables the weapon altogether,
	and <literal>1</literal> or higher specifies the maximum number of mortars per team.
    If desired, the maximum can be specified as a percentage of team players by suffixing
    <replaceable>num</replaceable> with a percent-symbol.
</para>
</refsection>

